Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.99,0:02:13.30,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,100)\fs50\pos(1055,1010)}Necro
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.30,0:02:16.37,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,100)}苦しみだけ置いていくはず
